Jean-Dieudonne Biog - Points

Jean-Dieudonne Biog scores a career high 23 points (2014)

On March 08, 2014, Jean-Dieudonne Biog set his career high in points in a France - Betclic Elite U21 game. That day he scored 23 points in ASVEL U21's home win against Nanterre U21, 96-75. He also had 14 rebounds, 2 steals and 3 blocks. He shot 9/13 from two, shooting at 69.2% from the field. He also shot 5/6 from the free-throw line.

Jean-Dieudonne Biog - Rebounds

Jean-Dieudonne Biog grabs a career high 16 rebounds (2013)

On April 08, 2013, Jean-Dieudonne Biog tied his career high in rebounds in a France - Betclic Elite U21 game. That day he grabbed 16 rebounds in ASVEL U21's home win against Strasbourg U21, 85-79. He also had 7 points, 5 assists, 1 steal.

Jean-Dieudonne Biog - Assists

Jean-Dieudonne Biog gives a career high 5 assists (2013)

On April 08, 2013, Jean-Dieudonne Biog set his career high in assists in a France - Betclic Elite U21 game. That day he dished 5 assists in ASVEL U21's home win against Strasbourg U21, 85-79. He also had 7 points, 16 rebounds, 1 steal.

Jean-Dieudonne Biog - Steals

Jean-Dieudonne Biog has a career high 3 steals (2015)

On January 20, 2015, Jean-Dieudonne Biog tied his career high in steals in a France - Betclic Elite U21 game. That day he reached 3 steals in ASVEL U21's home loss against Nancy U21, 51-65. He also had 2 points, 5 rebounds and 2 assists.

Jean-Dieudonne Biog - Blocks

Jean-Dieudonne Biog blocks a career high 5 shots (2014)

On October 24, 2014, Jean-Dieudonne Biog set his career high in blocks in a France - Betclic Elite U21 game. That day he went for 5 blocks in ASVEL U21's home win against Bourg-en-Bresse U21, 65-58. He also had 14 points, 7 rebounds and 2 assists.
